Seeding means uploading the data for other users even after you're done downloading, and not fucking off like most people do! Benefit of having more seeders is that you will have more amount of complete data to download from..

Leeching refers to uploading and downloading the data simultaneously! Leechers can only upload the data they are done downloading. So, if there are only leechers, you might not get the part of the data you are looking for, if they haven't done downloading that part yet.
